| {{GER-d}} [[Sebastian Vettel]]
| [[Red Bull Racing|Red Bull]]-[[Renault Sport|Renault]]
| 1 min 34 s 968
|
|-
| '''2'''
| {{GBR-d}} [[Jenson Button]]
| [[McLaren Racing|McLaren]]-[[Mercedes-Benz|Mercedes]]
